data.description: This home is waiting for new owner with open floorplan in a great location.  Large wrap around front porch on corner lot.  Backyard has large patio with wood fencing that offers lots of privacy.  Just minutes away from Concord Mills, restaurants, and 85.  There are a lot of unique features in this home such as arched doorway and squared columns.  Floorplan is great for entertaining.  Master suite is on the main level with remodeled updated Master bath.  House has very unique features.  Wide staircase leads up to second level where you will find an additional third bedroom, which is ideal for overnight guest.  There is a sliding glass door that leads out to a separate balcony  area.  This room can also be used for theatre or recreation space.
